Extremely happy to lay the foundation stone for Hong Fu’s non leather footwear unit at #SIPCOT Panappakkam in Ranipet district, with an investment of 1500 crores creating 25,000 jobs. This is the latest among the string of such investments in TamilNadu, attracted by our proactive outreach towards Taiwanese companies and pioneering footwear policy. 

In our mission to become the footwear capital of India, we are proud that we have been able to bring in a cumulative investment of Rs.6,550 crores in this sector, creating 86,150 job opportunities in the districts of Perambalur, Villupuram, Kallakurichi, Ariyalur and Ranipet. Another significant outcome is that most of these jobs will be for our young women!

